{"tid":10604,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"樓價恐怖過鬼！逾半申請者願住「凶宅」","createTime":"2016-11-29T04:16:31.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-29T05:37:30.000Z","uid":22869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5f5fa1a47bf9079c6dc741242b50b96e51f5004d","tid":10604,"uid":22869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T04:16:31.000Z","msg":"【住公屋做人生贏家】樓價恐怖過鬼！逾半申請者願住「凶宅」<br />\n<br />\n房委會完成2016年公屋申請者統計調查，除顯示大學生申請比例增加外，過五成申請者更「百無禁忌」，為加快「上樓」，表明有意參加特快配屋計劃，不介意住垃圾房隔離，甚至「凶宅」。<br />\n<br />\n房委會統計截至今年3月申請者分佈，截新登記配額及計分制的申請者平均年齡為32歲，逾半新申請者是30歲或以下。<br />\n至於擁有專上、大專或以上學歷的申請者佔整體47%，較2012年的34%大增；若只以30歲以下申請者計算，更有多達71%申請者擁有專上、大專或以上學歷。新登記配額及計分制申請者當中，46%於登記時是學生，30歲以下者的相應百分比為81%。<br />\n另外，今年有53%申請者表明不介意入住「特快配屋」，比例較2012年增7個百分點，數字創五年新高。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/finance/20161129/55979642\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Ffinance%2F20161129%2F55979642&d=ctOUxKLv%2B9zBCrzB%2FMEnrQT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=5656a743\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Ffinance%2F20161129%2F55979642&h=78d0d18b\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/finance/20161129/55979642</a>"},{"pid":"79b573a53fafe255b19cae987ba509633a8c9272","tid":10604,"uid":31071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T04:18:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"807d40f189cc1b819ebf4e9595372a84811000c2","tid":10604,"uid":36035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T04:30:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e8fe97d5d5493cc841d11f294be0aefc54991d96","tid":10604,"uid":1096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T05:02:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有返咁上下人生閱歷，社會經驗既人都知，呢個世界係冇鬼<br />\n<br />\n不過如果隔籬係癡線佬 / 婆，或者係垃圾收集房都幾頭痕</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n重衰過鬼"},{"pid":"ec3790e823e59a22f9145c77237c746930ebe6be","tid":10604,"uid":38390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T05:03:41.000Z","msg":"鬼都無屋住"},{"pid":"c3a866e1573c36cc443c5e384b1b23b06693d74e","tid":10604,"uid":1703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T05:32:19.000Z","msg":"冇野恐怖得過窮鬼"},{"pid":"92000a1e27d241fe2b2398684c57795c504d0f32","tid":10604,"uid":2086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T05:37:30.000Z","msg":"香港d樓價仲得人驚過鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}